    v2 = 1.0

    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.85))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = (wp.exp(v2) + (tmp - (v0 + 0.26 / v2 + 0.26)))
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.58) * 0.78) - 0.91)
    v0 = 0.24
